text: Joseph Crovetto (17 December 1889 - 27 March 1964) was a Monegasque gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1889 births Category:1964 deaths Category:Monegasque male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Monaco Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
